Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing out as I sink to the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathe out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and though I feel heavy as I leave\Nmy floatie of a body behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am being freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up at the bubbles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,as I let myself sink\Nuntil my back touched the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Swoosh, swoosh, swoosh, swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...\NSneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Swoosh, swoosh, swoosh, swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Distance"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:30.73,OS,,0,0,0,,"I'm thinking about stopping by\Nyour place today... You mind??!"\N\N"Adachi, can you do sit-ups???"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Adachi, can you do sit-ups???"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What even was that message just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's exactly how it sounds...\NI-I was wondering if you can do sit-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I just did one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. You see, I can't do any\Nunless someone holds down my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. That's it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, yup, yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Time" "Start" "Input" "Stop"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You just walked for five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. At least get\Nthe most out of this trial voucher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you been\Ngoing to school every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You see me leave every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean\Nyou're actually going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that's going\Nto suffer if you don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always taught you not to be a burden\Nto those around you, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said I know and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being a burden to others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one thing my mom\Nhad always drilled into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she feared that I'd end up\Na good-for-nothing in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, is the fact that I'm\Nfloating here actually burdening anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when I'm skipping school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just escaping being in\Na classroom because it feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck at the bottom of a well\Nand can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Classes will continue even if I'm not there,\Nwithout a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking up at the water's surface,\Nit turned everything blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded of the label of\Nthe mineral water Adachi drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a brilliant shade of aqua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, just that color and the reflections
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I joined this gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even I get some\Nexcellent ideas at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We did that last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is filled with grandpas and grandmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so even someone my age gets to enjoy\Nbeing the youngest and feeling superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you had to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm getting at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding. But it is rare\Nto see someone young like you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know you were here, Ms. Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, hello, Ms. Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... So this is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan is tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought I'd run\Ninto Adachi's mom in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,That coach is just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:04.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,Right? The other one's so much better. And they sound better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi hates talking about her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her lips tighten and she never really\Ntalks about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:09.24,On Top,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.\N Being younger isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel any warmth in how\NAdachi feels about her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how old is your daughter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's 15. A first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then things must be easier\Nnow that entrance exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They are, but she's such a troublemaker.\NI just don't know what to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She at least goes to school,\Nbut who knows if she's actually trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She never says what she's thinking.\NI just don't get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's such a depressing child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... know Ada... your daughter very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe you shouldn't\Ntalk about her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't understand her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because you haven't actually\Ntried to understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to start an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here with a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That really has nothing to do with this.\NThey're not going to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exactly know what's right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's have a competition\Nto decide what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever can stay in the sauna longer wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So just for today, I ask that you actually\Nbe a good mom to your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your way of being defiant or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it's been.\NThe ringing in my ears is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Adachi could never even imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that her mom and her classmate were
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:09:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,childishly duking it out in the sauna right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly is a good mom to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know because I've never been a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me your ideal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think just a normal mom would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like being with your kid and\Nhaving dinner with them, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to let you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to let me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's actually happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's actually happy,\NI wish she'd just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She just shuts herself off from everyone,\Nno matter where I take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea if she's having fun or anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She was probably five? Oh, maybe four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you thinking about the past?\NWhy not think about your daughter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one likes listening\Nto their mother at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go ahead let you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't this happen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But last time, you were doing this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs seem to keep twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Yup. It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So yesterday... My mom was being weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We had dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird... and sort of nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But also suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She always makes food for me,\Nbut we never eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's rarely ever home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I was so anxious that I had\Nno idea what the food tasted like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what all that was about though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're c-close...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really can smell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Adachi, do some sit-ups for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sit-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see up your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did I do something wrong?\NI was just trying to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! I was the only one who saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because that you saw\Nthat it's... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you can't do any sit-ups, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... was that supposed to be a sit-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess nothing can ever change in just a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed she seemed to be emitting the\Nsame kind of wavelengths as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This little weirdo is Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my friend, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have half, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nom, nom... Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister ended up naming\Nher peculiar friend "Yachi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:34.24,OS,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke, getting something to eat,\Nor the river..."\N\N"Where do you want to go???"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Shimamura? What's this message about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked karaoke.\NNagafuji wanted to eat somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hino wanted to go to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino invited me out next Sunday,\Nso I figured I'd invite you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... But wouldn't I make things awkward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you actually worry about stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I figured you probably\Ndidn't care about harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, I guess you're coming then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So wait, are we going to end up\Ngoing wherever I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Then karaoke, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go ahead and tell Hino and Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's-- O-Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Let's sing something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure... What should we sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Something you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Post Office"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always late to class,\Nbut you're actually on time to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how I feel hearing that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Hair's not here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? H-Hey, did you buy that outfit\Nat Shimamura? It looks great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize everyone makes that joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been great if you\Nwore your work outfit, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd actually show up, Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... Well, I had nothing better to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. You were bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You either sound like a high school kid\Nor death with that motive, so I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi, let's totes have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I'll get things started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ The void of time... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I'll actually put in a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Song Requests"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Dandelion"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind having fun with everyone\Nlike this, but something feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also seems like Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is forcing herself to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on her in a daze\Non the second floor of the gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That seemed more normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Shimamura and I have\Nthe difference of being good or bad at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we pretty much feel the same\Nwhen it comes to hanging out with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that we're so similar with that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're going in order, it should be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get another mic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Adachi and I are going to sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Adacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Adacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Song Name: {\i1}Merry-go-round{\i0}"\N"Send"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be helping me out if you sang with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like singing in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I'm with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.80,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,Round and round goes the merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:41.43,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to reach you, but I just can't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:46.31,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,Will there ever be a day that we'll overlap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:51.98,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,I hope you feel the same way, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:06.62,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,It's like the middle of a donut
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:14.34,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,You think there's something there,\Nbut it's nowhere to be found
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:19.97,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,The sweeter it gets, the more I want to peek
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:30.06,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,The moment I casually got on board,\Nthe bell rings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.85,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,I stared at you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.90,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,I was just staring off into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.78,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,Because we'll get dizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.74,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,All sparkly and all fluffy, we get closer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun, Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'd rather you just say my name normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like nicknames?\NWait, why am I the only one not allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't your house to the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:11.98,On Top Italic,,0,0,0,,But how do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have your usual mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and breezy near your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the view amazing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like doing stuff like that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't invite you anymore if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm not suffering or anything,\Nso please invite me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it seemed like you had\Nsomething you wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept looking at me at karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I staring that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think you were just imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes met so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bunch of things\NI want to say to Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I said any of them,\NI feel like she'd look at me weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or she'd run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all things like that,\Nso I just shrink back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And they just keep piling up...\Nand become stagnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a bunch of things\Njust dog-pile above my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when a fruit ripens and gathers nutrients,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but after some time,\Nit rots and falls to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a sapling sticking out of the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the end peeks out and tries to escape my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I held it back, but I was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you pat me on the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even look up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I overcame these feelings of regrets mixed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with something else many times and despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, I still looked forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you like being coddled, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like time and the Earth had just\Ncome to a stop and were staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how fast my heart was beating,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart was so calm\NI almost wanted to cry softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy right now from a girl\Nfrom my class patting me on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with me? Am I stupid? Am I weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's actually a little bit of both...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Big Sis in class, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, give me your can.\NI'll go throw it away for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's still some left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied. The can was actually empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be someone special to Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean that in a weird way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I actually was special to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:52.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 4: 'High School Girls On Holiday'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the realization\Nthat I guess I really do like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:07.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'Adachi's Question'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Karaoke!{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment when you're singing your\Nheart out and the employee comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Clack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:23:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! The real employee just showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the employee, Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your point?!
